# CrowdSec Hybrid Agent - Environment Variables

Rename this to `.env` and adjust the paths to match your server setup.

| Variable | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| `TZ` | Timezone (e.g., Asia/Kuala_Lumpur) |
| `GID` | System Group ID (run `id` on host) |
| `NPM_LOGS_DIR` | Path to NPM access logs directory |
| `CROWDSEC_LAPI_PORT` | Local API port (default: 8082) |
| `API_KEY` | API key for the host firewall bouncer |

```bash
TZ=Asia/Kuala_Lumpur
GID=1000
NPM_LOGS_DIR=/path/to/your/npm/data/logs
CROWDSEC_LAPI_PORT=8082
API_KEY=your_api_key_here
```